data.description: Welcome to 1224 Seaside Cove Ln, a stunning property located in the highly sought-after Katy ISD school district of Katy, Texas. This exceptional home is perfect for those seeking the ideal combination of luxury, comfort, and convenience. This 3-bedroom, 2-bathroom home boasts a generously sized primary suite offering a peaceful retreat with its spa-like en-suite bathroom. You’ll find a built-in home office at the center of the house that combines functionality, style, and practicality to create a well-integrated workspace. It brings convenience, efficiency, and a touch of sophistication to daily tasks, enhancing both professional productivity and the overall harmony of the living environment. The chef-inspired kitchen features stainless steel appliances, granite countertops, a walk-in pantry, and a large center island, providing ample space for culinary adventures.    Schedule a showing today at 1224 Seaside Cove Ln, Katy, Texas 77493.
